        "created_at": "2017-11-27T14:55:08.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Approximately $25 per 375ml, for essentially an off-label Cotes du Rhone, a la Rudy and John?   Ouch!<br>\nThat is even MORE profligate than my $35 1991 Beringer Knights Valley CS (750ml).    <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/3/3bd35321ffd7ed2243d1d518ebb606d554360600.gif\" width=\"50\" height=\"22\" alt=\"neener\" title=\"[neener.gif]\"><br>\nDon\u2019t be cheap.  Buy the real LMHB.    <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/7/7d450e9830889c8943b674446a21b7254cad657e.gif\" width=\"18\" height=\"20\" alt=\"[wow.gif]\" title=\"wow\"></p>",
