        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/arv_r/{size}/76949_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-12-01T22:47:43.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I chewed through cases of the 1998 and 2000 and felt \u2013 over time \u2013 they were fairly classical in Graves charry/smoky notes.</p>\n<p>How close are they to LMHB?  I don\u2019t know - that elixir doesn\u2019t cross my lips enough to make informed comparisons.</p>\n<p>Maybe they are just too young.</p>",
