        "created_at": "2017-12-01T23:22:57.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Arv R\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Arv R:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I chewed through cases of the 1998 and 2000 and felt \u2013 over time \u2013 they were fairly classical in Graves charry/smoky notes.</p>\n<p>How close are they to LMHB?  I don\u2019t know - that elixir doesn\u2019t cross my lips enough to make informed comparisons.</p>\n<p>Maybe they are just too young.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>There have been some pretty noticeable stylistic changes at LMHB and HB since the younger Delmas took over. I don\u2019t think they\u2019re just too young.</p>",
